@startuml A4_00_flow_overview_simple
title Runtime Flows – Simplified Overview

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

actor Student
participant "Agent Service" as AGENT
participant "RAG Service" as RAG
participant "Enrollment Service" as ENROLLMENT
database "Postgres" as DB
database "Neo4j" as NEO4J

== Session Setup ==
Student -> AGENT : login / create session
AGENT -> DB : create session
AGENT --> Student : session token

== Enrollment Question ==
Student -> AGENT : enrollment question
AGENT -> RAG : policy search (if needed)
RAG --> AGENT : policy context
AGENT -> ENROLLMENT : enrollment tool call
ENROLLMENT -> DB : query data
ENROLLMENT -> NEO4J : query graph
ENROLLMENT --> AGENT : results
AGENT --> Student : response

== Document Upload ==
Student -> AGENT : upload document
AGENT -> RAG : process document
RAG -> DB : store vectors
RAG --> AGENT : document ready

note right of Student
**Main Flows:**
- Session & authentication
- Enrollment questions
- Document ingestion
- Chat with context
end note

@enduml

